==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ennoblement
<hw>En*no"ble*ment</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of
making noble, or of exalting, dignifying, or advancing to
nobility.</def> <rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which ennobles; excellence; dignity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ennobler</ent>⟦br⟧
